data.description: SELLERS GIVING CONCESSION FOR 2-1 BUYDOWN TO GET YOUR BUYERS’ RATES INTO THE 5S OR 6S! Come check out this amazing unique home!  The home sits on one of the larger lots in the whole development while also being located on a Cul de Sac.  Custom touches can be found throughout the home: sprawling open concepts, butler's pantry, enormous walk in closets and more.  All bedrooms can be found upstairs while the downstairs boasts a large kitchen that overlooks the living room while the office and formal dining flank the entryway. With just under a quarter acre lot, the backyard is a great place to enjoy the cooler days we have coming up.
